<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.223877>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A – G. Taranis adenensis sp. nov. A. Holotype, scale bar 800 μm, Gulf of Aden, stn RED SED S 92 / 1 (MZB 49753); B – G. Paratype, Gulf of Aden, stn RED SED 92 / 1 (MZB 49754); B. Frontal view, scale bar 600 μm; C. Apical view, scale bar 400 μm; D. Penultimate whorl, scale bar 200 μm; E. Surface microsculpture, scale bar 40 μm; F – G. Protoconch, scale bar 100 μm. H – N. Mioawateria vivens sp. nov. H. Holotype, 6.3 x 3.3 mm, Gulf of Aden, stn RED SED 92 / 1 (MZB 49755); I – N. Paratype, Red Sea, stn RED SED 92 / 4 (MZB 49756); I. Frontal view, scale bar 1 mm; J. Apical view, scale bar 1 mm; K – L. Protoconch, scale bar 100 μm; M. Detail of protoconch I, scale bar 50 μm; N. Surface microsculpture, scale bar 50 μm. O – T. Holotype of Awheaturris lozoueti sp. nov., Philippines, AURORA 2007 stn CP 2682 (MNHN 25730); O. Frontal view, scale bar 1 mm; P. Apical view, scale bar 1 mm; Q. Penultimate whorl, scale bar 500 μm; R. Surface microsculpture, scale bar 80 μm; S – T. Protoconch, scale bar 200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/223877/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

